## Enforcement

- **Before coding**: Always check the workflow diagram first
- **During coding**: Follow the documented data flow and integration points
- **After coding**: Update the workflow diagram if implementation differs
- **Status updates**: Change 🚧 to ✅ when page is fully implemented

---

## Exceptions

- **Minor bug fixes**: Don't require workflow diagram updates for small bug fixes
- **UI-only changes**: Don't require updates if only UI/styling changes (no data flow changes)
- **Performance optimizations**: Don't require updates if only performance improvements (no functional changes)

